description: Defines the 'Budget' data model class with JSON serialization/deserialization methods used in the expense frontend of the budget tracker project.

classes.name: Budget
classes.description: A data model representing a budget with properties like id, categoryId, limit, spent, periodStart, and periodEnd, including methods for JSON serialization.

methods.name: Budget.fromJson
methods.description: Factory constructor to create a Budget instance from a JSON map.

methods.name: toJson
methods.description: Converts the Budget instance to a JSON map.
